[
  {
    "startTime": 0.344,
    "endTime": 1.6560000000000001,
    "text": "- Wait, what the heck?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.656,
    "endTime": 3.607,
    "text": "Why do you-- why do both of you think that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.608,
    "endTime": 6.627000000000001,
    "text": "I mean, okay guess I'm learning things about myself today."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.627,
    "endTime": 9.294,
    "text": "(playful music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.672,
    "endTime": 13.569,
    "text": "We are here to see who knows me best,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.569,
    "endTime": 15.110000000000001,
    "text": "my boyfriend or my dad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.11,
    "endTime": 16.204,
    "text": "- So we're figuring out who knows me better,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.204,
    "endTime": 18.171,
    "text": "my mom or my boyfriend Carlos."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.171,
    "endTime": 19.778,
    "text": "- My boyfriend Dakota and I have been together"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.778,
    "endTime": 22.93,
    "text": "for about four and a half years."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.93,
    "endTime": 25.8,
    "text": "- Carlos and I have been dating for two years and a week."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.8,
    "endTime": 26.487000000000002,
    "text": "'Cause we just had our anniversary last week."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.487,
    "endTime": 28.546,
    "text": "- I would say he knows me way better than my dad,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.547,
    "endTime": 30.61,
    "text": "my dad has obviously been there for like,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.61,
    "endTime": 31.747,
    "text": "all those monumental life moments,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.747,
    "endTime": 32.881,
    "text": "but all the details and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.881,
    "endTime": 34.14,
    "text": "the nitty-gritty stuff about my life,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.14,
    "endTime": 35.612,
    "text": "my boyfriend definitely knows me better."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.612,
    "endTime": 36.668,
    "text": "- After you date somebody for a while,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.668,
    "endTime": 39.1,
    "text": "you just kinda like-- lives just start to meld."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.1,
    "endTime": 41.351,
    "text": "- I hope Dakota would, if he doesn't know"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.351,
    "endTime": 43.281,
    "text": "the majority of things about me that kinda sucks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.281,
    "endTime": 44.881,
    "text": "We've been together for so long."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.881,
    "endTime": 46.599000000000004,
    "text": "- I feel like they're gonna be very mixed,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.599,
    "endTime": 48.433,
    "text": "like my mom is probably gonna go with like,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.433,
    "endTime": 50.758,
    "text": "answers that would have applied when I was like 12."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.758,
    "endTime": 52.327000000000005,
    "text": "And then my boyfriend knows me better now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.327,
    "endTime": 53.607,
    "text": "- My dad and I are really close."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.607,
    "endTime": 55.345,
    "text": "I go down to see him every single weekend."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.345,
    "endTime": 57.841,
    "text": "We spend like, almost every single meal together"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.841,
    "endTime": 58.897,
    "text": "when I'm down there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.897,
    "endTime": 60.156,
    "text": "- So my mom and I are really close,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.156,
    "endTime": 62.573,
    "text": "we talk pretty much everyday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.942,
    "endTime": 65.31,
    "text": "I call her like, every single break that I have."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.31,
    "endTime": 65.864,
    "text": "I don't know why, like,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.864,
    "endTime": 67.955,
    "text": "I don't consider myself a momma's boy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.955,
    "endTime": 70.612,
    "text": "but looking at it from an outsider perspective,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.612,
    "endTime": 71.743,
    "text": "I probably am."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.743,
    "endTime": 72.937,
    "text": "- Let's see who wins."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.937,
    "endTime": 75.52,
    "text": "(upbeat music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.831,
    "endTime": 78.664,
    "text": "- Question number one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.817,
    "endTime": 80.89899999999999,
    "text": "What is my favorite meal?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.303,
    "endTime": 83.886,
    "text": "- Did you write it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.447,
    "endTime": 86.2,
    "text": "- That's not a meal, actually."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.2,
    "endTime": 88.5,
    "text": "- Okay I didn't know this was that hard of a question."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.5,
    "endTime": 89.642,
    "text": "- You guys ready?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.642,
    "endTime": 90.892,
    "text": "Three, two one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.584,
    "endTime": 93.417,
    "text": "No, what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.562,
    "endTime": 96.148,
    "text": "(laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.148,
    "endTime": 97.832,
    "text": "That's your favorite food."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.832,
    "endTime": 99.53899999999999,
    "text": "This is not gonna go well."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.54,
    "endTime": 101.4,
    "text": "- One, two, three."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.686,
    "endTime": 104.36200000000001,
    "text": "Oh, what? (laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.362,
    "endTime": 105.838,
    "text": "- That was a close guess though."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.838,
    "endTime": 107.338,
    "text": "- Yeah she eat that every morning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.338,
    "endTime": 108.69,
    "text": "- Yeah, that's why this question is so hard"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.691,
    "endTime": 111.242,
    "text": "is 'cause she changes her mind all the time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.242,
    "endTime": 113.684,
    "text": "So it's not what she has liked, historically."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.684,
    "endTime": 115.262,
    "text": "- Historically? (laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.263,
    "endTime": 117.384,
    "text": "- It's like, what're you feeling right now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.384,
    "endTime": 118.813,
    "text": "So for lunch you wanna get poke,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.813,
    "endTime": 119.668,
    "text": "is that what you're saying?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.668,
    "endTime": 120.501,
    "text": "- Yeah. - Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.501,
    "endTime": 123.352,
    "text": "- If I won the lottery, what's the first thing I would buy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.352,
    "endTime": 124.72800000000001,
    "text": "I feel like it's really easy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.728,
    "endTime": 125.67599999999999,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.677,
    "endTime": 126.90400000000001,
    "text": "- That's not hard."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.904,
    "endTime": 128.332,
    "text": "- Okay we gotta start off slow"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.332,
    "endTime": 130.114,
    "text": "and then we'll get into the hard ones."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.114,
    "endTime": 131.213,
    "text": "You get too confident and then"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.213,
    "endTime": 132.727,
    "text": "it's gonna bite you in the butt later."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.728,
    "endTime": 133.751,
    "text": "- Okay. (laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.751,
    "endTime": 135.74,
    "text": "- You're answering really quickly I feel like you're not"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.74,
    "endTime": 136.679,
    "text": "- I don't want to overthink it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.679,
    "endTime": 137.905,
    "text": "- Yeah you're not thinking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.905,
    "endTime": 139.207,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.207,
    "endTime": 140.775,
    "text": "- It better be this answer,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.775,
    "endTime": 142.449,
    "text": "if its not I didn't teach you too well."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.449,
    "endTime": 145.40400000000002,
    "text": "- I don't know anymore, it's making me nervous. (laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.404,
    "endTime": 146.904,
    "text": "- Three, two, one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.226,
    "endTime": 149.601,
    "text": "A house and clothes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.601,
    "endTime": 151.146,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.146,
    "endTime": 151.97799999999998,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.207,
    "endTime": 154.828,
    "text": "- C'mon you know you'd buy a house."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.828,
    "endTime": 156.703,
    "text": "- So it's zero, zero. Alright."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.703,
    "endTime": 157.56900000000002,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.569,
    "endTime": 158.402,
    "text": "Great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.63,
    "endTime": 160.375,
    "text": "- One, two, three."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.375,
    "endTime": 161.697,
    "text": "Oh yeah, it's a house!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.697,
    "endTime": 162.868,
    "text": "- Father knows best."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.868,
    "endTime": 163.701,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.701,
    "endTime": 164.535,
    "text": "- And boyfriend."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.535,
    "endTime": 167.381,
    "text": "- What's my favorite way to relax and recharge my batteries?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.381,
    "endTime": 169.591,
    "text": "I guess 'cause I don't, no one knows how to answer it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.591,
    "endTime": 171.82000000000002,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.82,
    "endTime": 172.983,
    "text": "- I'm still not overthinking this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.983,
    "endTime": 174.199,
    "text": "Don't overthink it Wolfie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.199,
    "endTime": 175.532,
    "text": "- Oh, it's easy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.713,
    "endTime": 178.54,
    "text": "- I feel like my handwriting's getting sloppier now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.54,
    "endTime": 180.623,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.863,
    "endTime": 183.52,
    "text": "- This is not going well,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.52,
    "endTime": 185.728,
    "text": "I am now putting myself up for adoption and then single."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.729,
    "endTime": 186.603,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.603,
    "endTime": 187.76500000000001,
    "text": "And three, two, one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.765,
    "endTime": 189.547,
    "text": "- Oh, I put (laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.548,
    "endTime": 190.951,
    "text": "- Well that actually would be the right answer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.951,
    "endTime": 191.784,
    "text": "- Meditation!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.784,
    "endTime": 193.16199999999998,
    "text": "- Wait I wanna change mine, - Oh shit!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.163,
    "endTime": 194.816,
    "text": "because that's actually true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.816,
    "endTime": 196.725,
    "text": "I didn't-- but meditating on the beach."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.725,
    "endTime": 198.642,
    "text": "- See, we know you more"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.658,
    "endTime": 199.82299999999998,
    "text": "than you know yourself. - Yeah, you know me better"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.824,
    "endTime": 201.824,
    "text": "than I know me. Clearly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.72,
    "endTime": 204.72,
    "text": "- Oh, I put sleep, babe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.815,
    "endTime": 207.322,
    "text": "- Yeah I know, you guys both got a point."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.322,
    "endTime": 208.28,
    "text": "- One to one. Yeah! - That was good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.28,
    "endTime": 211.5,
    "text": "I'll have to do some introspective time after this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.5,
    "endTime": 214.677,
    "text": "- Would I consider myself more of an introvert or extrovert?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.677,
    "endTime": 216.34,
    "text": "I feel like that one's pretty easy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.341,
    "endTime": 217.983,
    "text": "- What if I just throw it and write the wrong one?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.983,
    "endTime": 218.954,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.954,
    "endTime": 220.287,
    "text": "Three, two, one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.436,
    "endTime": 222.269,
    "text": "Extrovert."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.484,
    "endTime": 223.317,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.317,
    "endTime": 224.15,
    "text": "- Oh dang."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.15,
    "endTime": 225.25400000000002,
    "text": "- I got it wrong. - Are you serious?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.254,
    "endTime": 226.671,
    "text": "- I got it wrong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.694,
    "endTime": 228.194,
    "text": "- One, two, three."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.655,
    "endTime": 229.488,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.903,
    "endTime": 230.736,
    "text": "- Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.977,
    "endTime": 232.315,
    "text": "- Wait, what the heck?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.315,
    "endTime": 234.21,
    "text": "Why do you-- why do both of you think that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.211,
    "endTime": 236.638,
    "text": "- Because regularly people think that you're an extrovert,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.638,
    "endTime": 237.579,
    "text": "but actually--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.579,
    "endTime": 238.412,
    "text": "- Exactly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.412,
    "endTime": 240.222,
    "text": "- You're a natural introvert."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.222,
    "endTime": 242.401,
    "text": "- You like to spend time with yourself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.401,
    "endTime": 246.15,
    "text": "- I mean, okay guess I'm learning things about myself today."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.15,
    "endTime": 248.412,
    "text": "- What do you think is my worst trait?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.413,
    "endTime": 249.30100000000002,
    "text": "I don't like that question."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.301,
    "endTime": 250.928,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.929,
    "endTime": 252.296,
    "text": "feel free to offend me, we'll see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.296,
    "endTime": 253.129,
    "text": "- Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.129,
    "endTime": 255.28,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.28,
    "endTime": 256.959,
    "text": "- What do we think, or what do you think?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.959,
    "endTime": 258.459,
    "text": "- What do I think?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.845,
    "endTime": 259.71700000000004,
    "text": "- You ready? You can show it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.716,
    "endTime": 261.279,
    "text": "- I didn't answer this, um--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.279,
    "endTime": 262.242,
    "text": "- Grouchiness?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.242,
    "endTime": 263.168,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.168,
    "endTime": 264.39300000000003,
    "text": "That is so mean!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.393,
    "endTime": 265.349,
    "text": "- He's a kiss up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.349,
    "endTime": 266.438,
    "text": "- I had to win."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.439,
    "endTime": 267.54900000000004,
    "text": "It's two-one. - I'm not grouchy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.549,
    "endTime": 269.304,
    "text": "- Oh, you're never grouchy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.304,
    "endTime": 271.55999999999995,
    "text": "- What? No, Carlos gets that point."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.57,
    "endTime": 271.939,
    "text": "Can he get that point?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.939,
    "endTime": 273.156,
    "text": "- Oh, Dakota got it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.156,
    "endTime": 275.777,
    "text": "I'm too bossy. (laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.777,
    "endTime": 277.419,
    "text": "Are you sad 'cause I boss you around a lot?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.42,
    "endTime": 279.7,
    "text": "- What type of adventure would I prefer?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.7,
    "endTime": 282.4,
    "text": "A spontaneous one or a carefully planned out one?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.4,
    "endTime": 283.55699999999996,
    "text": "- Do you feel confident about this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.557,
    "endTime": 285.13,
    "text": "- Very confident. - Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.13,
    "endTime": 286.513,
    "text": "- One, two, three."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.492,
    "endTime": 288.32500000000005,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.325,
    "endTime": 289.158,
    "text": "- Oh, you got it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.158,
    "endTime": 290.33500000000004,
    "text": "- Why'd you put spontaneous?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.335,
    "endTime": 292.305,
    "text": "- Well 'cause you like to be spontaneous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.305,
    "endTime": 294.29200000000003,
    "text": "You want me to plan things out for you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.292,
    "endTime": 295.799,
    "text": "and just kinda let you..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.8,
    "endTime": 296.63300000000004,
    "text": "- No but--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.633,
    "endTime": 297.488,
    "text": "- But it's still planned out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.488,
    "endTime": 300.206,
    "text": "- I'm planning it out but for you it's spontaneous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.206,
    "endTime": 301.333,
    "text": "Because you have no idea."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.333,
    "endTime": 303.63300000000004,
    "text": "- I mean I guess, but I need someone to plan something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.633,
    "endTime": 305.11899999999997,
    "text": "- Planned, yeah. - Planned. Ding."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.119,
    "endTime": 306.44800000000004,
    "text": "- What frightens me most?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.448,
    "endTime": 307.873,
    "text": "- There's no multiple choice answer?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.874,
    "endTime": 309.99,
    "text": "- No. (laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.99,
    "endTime": 310.353,
    "text": "And you only choose one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.353,
    "endTime": 311.77,
    "text": "- Wait, only one?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 311.787,
    "endTime": 314.936,
    "text": "- Yeah, do you think I'm scared of multiple things?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.937,
    "endTime": 315.77000000000004,
    "text": "Well, frightened."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.77,
    "endTime": 317.578,
    "text": "Frightened is different than scared."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 317.578,
    "endTime": 318.411,
    "text": "- That's easy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.411,
    "endTime": 319.244,
    "text": "- You think it's easy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.244,
    "endTime": 320.341,
    "text": "- I don think either of you will get it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.341,
    "endTime": 321.17400000000004,
    "text": "- Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.4,
    "endTime": 322.837,
    "text": "- So you're just writing anything?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.837,
    "endTime": 323.67,
    "text": "Great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.67,
    "endTime": 324.522,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.522,
    "endTime": 326.98,
    "text": "- [Woman] You're still thinking about it after you wrote it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 326.98,
    "endTime": 326.93100000000004,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 326.931,
    "endTime": 327.764,
    "text": "- Yeah, I'm ready."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.764,
    "endTime": 329.637,
    "text": "- Okay. One, two, three."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.637,
    "endTime": 330.72,
    "text": "I put my dad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.595,
    "endTime": 332.42800000000005,
    "text": "Spiders?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.428,
    "endTime": 334.2,
    "text": "- I actually probably should have guessed that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.2,
    "endTime": 334.835,
    "text": "- Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.835,
    "endTime": 336.248,
    "text": "- But you're scared of this all the time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.249,
    "endTime": 337.646,
    "text": "- Yeah, but I'm scared of you more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.646,
    "endTime": 338.795,
    "text": "- No that's respect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.795,
    "endTime": 340.30400000000003,
    "text": "- No. (laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.304,
    "endTime": 342.53999999999996,
    "text": "- On three, two, one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.252,
    "endTime": 343.25100000000003,
    "text": "- I'm rather boring here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 343.251,
    "endTime": 344.84,
    "text": "- Alright."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.84,
    "endTime": 345.52,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.52,
    "endTime": 346.292,
    "text": "- Oh you got it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346.292,
    "endTime": 347.89,
    "text": "- [Debbie] Disappointing others."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.89,
    "endTime": 349.801,
    "text": "- Only you spelled disappointing right, I didn't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.801,
    "endTime": 350.634,
    "text": "- Did I spell it..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 350.634,
    "endTime": 351.46700000000004,
    "text": "- [Man] So yeah, you got it right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.467,
    "endTime": 354.383,
    "text": "- Wow. What a deep profound answer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 354.677,
    "endTime": 355.833,
    "text": "I was gonna put like,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.833,
    "endTime": 356.66600000000005,
    "text": "- That was impressive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 356.666,
    "endTime": 357.888,
    "text": "- black cats or something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.888,
    "endTime": 359.359,
    "text": "- (laughs) Black cats."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 359.359,
    "endTime": 361.508,
    "text": "- Why would I be scared of-- I love cats."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 361.509,
    "endTime": 363.271,
    "text": "- I guess I didn't even want to take a risk on that one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.271,
    "endTime": 366.108,
    "text": "- Father's know best, I'm telling you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.108,
    "endTime": 368.5,
    "text": "- Four and a half years and you can't even win a game."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 368.5,
    "endTime": 368.883,
    "text": "So sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 369.58,
    "endTime": 371.61899999999997,
    "text": "- Alright I did pretty good though."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 371.619,
    "endTime": 373.29900000000004,
    "text": "- Yeah you did, you actually did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 373.299,
    "endTime": 374.132,
    "text": "- We were neck and neck."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.132,
    "endTime": 375.882,
    "text": "- And some of these questions were hard actually."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 375.882,
    "endTime": 376.71500000000003,
    "text": "- Yay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 379.302,
    "endTime": 380.13500000000005,
    "text": "Well done."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 380.135,
    "endTime": 381.594,
    "text": "I'm actually very surprised that my dad won."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 381.595,
    "endTime": 383.947,
    "text": "I'm surprised they could both answer some of the questions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383.947,
    "endTime": 385.769,
    "text": "'Cause I felt like some of them were really hard"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 385.769,
    "endTime": 387.628,
    "text": "and like super, super specific."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.628,
    "endTime": 388.878,
    "text": "- Sorry Debbie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 388.92,
    "endTime": 390.707,
    "text": "- Well done Carlos. - It was a good attempt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 390.707,
    "endTime": 392.539,
    "text": "You both know me better than I know myself. (laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392.539,
    "endTime": 393.808,
    "text": "So that was the important part."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 393.808,
    "endTime": 395.257,
    "text": "- So yeah, I'm surprised."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 395.257,
    "endTime": 396.9,
    "text": "- I'm not surprised. - I guess we are closer"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 396.9,
    "endTime": 397.714,
    "text": "than I think we are. (laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 397.714,
    "endTime": 398.872,
    "text": "- I'm not surprised."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.872,
    "endTime": 400.87100000000004,
    "text": "- Okay the game's over you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 400.871,
    "endTime": 402.568,
    "text": "don't have to be mean to each other."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.568,
    "endTime": 403.448,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.449,
    "endTime": 406.116,
    "text": "(playful music)"
  }
]